ks Eddy to help clear the [[tree]] that fell in front of Loopy's house from the heavy snow that came last night. But Eddy pretends to be sick and stays home reading [[comic books]]. Hearing of Eddy's illness, Loopy makes a visit to Eddy's house with her home-made cake only to find that he was faking his illness. Everyone becomes very disappointed in Eddy for pretending to be sick ...\n|December 12, 2003\n|-\n|}\n\n== Season 2 (2005-06) ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Episodes Number\n!Title\n!Synopsis\n!Airdate\n|-\n|1.\n|Hello, Friends\n|\n|December 3, 2005\n|-\n|2.\n|Petty's House\n|\n|December 4, 2005\n|-\n|3.\n|Learning How to Swim\n|\n|December 10, 2005\n|-\n|4.\n|Poby the Photographer\n|\n|December 11, 2005\n|-\n|5.\n|It's a Dinosaur!\n|\n|December 17, 2005\n|-\n|6.\n|Sailing in the Forest\n|\n|December 18, 2004\n|-\n|7.\n|My Name is Harry\n|\n|December 24, 2006\n|-\n|8.\n|I Love Singing\n|\n|December 25, 2005\n|-\n|9.\n|Crong the Great Painter\n|\n|December 31, 2005\n|-\n|10.\n|A Pretty Hair Pin\n|\n|January 1, 2006\n|-\n|11.\n|I Can Fly\n|\n|January 7, 2006\n|-\n|12.\n|I Envy You\n|\n|January 8, 2006\n|-\n|13.\n|The Biggest Snowman\n|\n|January 14, 2006\n|-\n|14.\n|Petty, You are So Cool!\n|\n|January 15, 2006\n|-\n|15.\n|Pororo Shrunk\n|\n|January 21, 2006\n|-\n|16.\n|Shark Attack!\n|\n|January 22, 2006\n|-\n|17.\n|Crong's First Word\n|\n|January 28, 2006\n|-\n|18.\n|Shhh, It is a Screat!\n|\n|January 29, 2006\n|-\n|19.\n|Who Did This!\n|\n|February 4, 2006\n|-\n|20.\n|The Genius Cook\n|\n|February 5, 2006\n|-\n|21.\n|Thanks, Harry!\n|\n|February 11, 2006\n|-\n|22.\n|I Am Not a Bed-Wetter!\n|\n|February 12, 2006\n|-\n|23.\n|I'm Super Crong\n|\n|February 18, 2006\n|-\n|24.\n|Snow White, Loopy\n|\n|February 19, 2006\n|-\n|25.\n|Eddy on the Moon\n|\n|February 25, 2006\n|-\n|26.\n|Crong Meets with a Seal\n|\n|February 26, 2006\n|-\n|27.\n|My Toy Fellas\n|\n|March 4, 2006\n|-\n|28.\n|Loopy and Petty\n|\n|March 5, 2006\n|-\n|29.\n|Scary Cookies\n|\n|March 11, 2006\n